the amazing power of drivel as a university professor of human resource development and an anglican brother , the amazing power of deliberate intent is pure drivel and has no redeeming value whatsoever . if you enjoy new-age fantasy , get a copy from your local library otherwise do not waste your money . if you are serious about spiritual growth you might read works such as the rule of benedict : insights for the ages , or the best selling book on spiritual development of all time.. it 's called the bible